+- **Already-claimed tasks complete.** A claimed task at
+  termination time can still be submitted, accepted, or rejected
+  normally; termination doesn't invalidate in-progress work. A
+  reclaim of a still-claimed task IS allowed (the resulting
+  pending task is unreachable, but reclaim itself is a Store-
+  level cleanup op that is not blocked).
